title: Dmytro Shcherbak
text:
Dmytro Shcherbak (; born 8 December 1996) is a <a href="Ukraine">Ukrainian</a> <a href="association%20football">football</a> player who played for <a href="FC%20Vorskla%20Poltava">Vorskla Poltava</a>.
Club career.
He made his <a href="Russian%20Premier%20League">Russian Premier League</a> debut for <a href="FC%20Anzhi%20Makhachkala">FC Anzhi Makhachkala</a> on 5 December 2016 in a game against <a href="FC%20Arsenal%20Tula">FC Arsenal Tula</a>.
